    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Q1) How do I destroy enemies?

    Every enemy has a equation above it.
    Look at the options on the enemy''s busy and Left-Click to shoot the area that
    shows the correct answer.


    Q2) What happens if I shoot the wrong answer?

    Shooting
    the wrong area will cause the enemy to increase its speed.


    Q3) Can enemies
    destroy my items?

    Yes. They can target your objects. so you must mine more
    wood and rebuild.

'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
